title: More teams we can “Stick a Fork in” & TNF preview
itunes:title: More teams we can “Stick a Fork in” & TNF preview
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Chris Wesseling & Gregg Rosenthal – recap the Cardinals dominant 28-3 victory over the Jets on Monday night before breaking down all the news from around the NFL; including Big Ben’s injury, and the latest on the Cowboys quarterback situation. Then, the heroes discuss a few more teams they think have no shot at the playoffs after Week 6, and decide which they're ready to "stick a fork" in. Finally, the heroes preview the Thursday night matchup at Lambeau Field between the Bears and the Packers.
